    "body": "@hefgi Agree this would be nice, especially for truffle init. Cross referencing to [truffle-core 117](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle-core/issues/117) which would solve several other issues as well.\r\n\r\n**Workaround**\r\n```\r\n# From within a project that already has lots of contents\r\nmkdir truffle-bare\r\ncd truffle-bare\r\ntruffle init\r\ncd ..\r\nmv truffle-bare/* .\r\nrm -rf truffle-bare\r\n```",
